# Cohort platform (Next.js)

Full guide: [execution/marketing/site/AGENTS.md](../../execution/marketing/site/AGENTS.md)

## Stack

Next.js 15 App Router · Firebase Auth (GitHub) · firebase-admin in API routes only · CSS modules (`app/page.module.css`)

## Critical split

```typescript
// ✅ Client component — types/format only
import type { CohortStats } from '@/lib/cohort-stats-types';

// ❌ Never in 'use client' files
import { getCohortStats } from '@/lib/cohort-stats-server';
```

## Peer review (implemented)

1. Written review: GitHub issue `Review by @{voter}` → `POST .../written-reviews`
2. Vote: `POST .../ratings` with `'up'|'down'` — 403 if no written review
3. UI: collapsed accordion in `PeerReviewCard.tsx`
4. Staff tally (post review week): `node scripts/tally-votes.mjs --project=<slug>`

## Program text

Edit `content/program.ts`; personalize with `personalizeProgramText()` for `{peerCount}`, `{org}`, `{handle}`.

## Env

Copy `.env.example` → `.env.local`. Service account at `secrets/` (gitignored).
